snippet.title: Warframe | The Deadlock Protocol Update Trailer - Available Now!
snippet.description: The Deadlock Protocol update sheds new light on the origins of the Corpus, introduces the time-bending Warframe, Protea and includes a remastered Corpus fleet full of innovative threats and escalating security measures. Available now on all platforms! Learn more: http://wrfr.me/deadlock #warframe #thedeadlockprotocol
